Author: audreyhepburnwho
Text: Yah i had about two years of stretching out paychecks and it definitely reduced binging. There was no way i could order in, or go out too often or even go crazy at the store. About two year's ago i got a well paying job and moved out and in the beginning i was saving a lot every month but, it got worse and worse to the point where i was ordering in multiple times a week to binge and not. Only did i gain a lot of weight i lost a lot of money. I eventually made it a rule that IF im gonna binge im gonna have to go to the store which can also be expensive but not as much as delivery. I cringe thinking how much money I've spent on takeout and delivered food just to binge...
